2) Evaluation against that preference:
- MUMFORD & SONS — Sigh No More (category: Folk; Traditional Folk): This album is folk-rooted, built around acoustic instrumentation (guitars, banjo, vocal harmonies) and dynamic arrangements that create a strong album flow. It contains well-known, punchy singles ("Little Lion Man," "The Cave") and a sonic variety across tracks that tends to reward focused listening from start to finish — qualities that make for an engaging CD listen and good replay value for someone who enjoys the CD medium.
